name: Dark Jedi Lightsaber (V)
Lore: 'Multifaceted jewels focus light into a deadly blade. Projects a meterlong beam of pure energy. A lightsaber is constructed personally by a Jedi as a part of training.',
Text: 'Deploy on Aurra Sing or Sidious. May add 1 to Force drain at an [Episode I] site where present. May target a character or creature for free. Draw two destiny. Add number of Jedi present. Target hit, and its forfeit = 0, if total destiny > defense value.',
